			<div class="content" id="post-content-294414">
									

<p>Okay, changed the Wanderlust characters to fit continuity. I basically combined Gruber and AA into Underwood, and changed Maddox into Trevino, and referenced AA's log in a more natural way.</p>
<p>Actually this streamlines things a bit for me, too.</p>

